PublicDescription: Predicted conditional branch executed.This event counts when any branch which can be predicted by the woke conditional predictor is retired. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off
BriefDescription: Predicted conditional branch executed.This event counts when any branch which can be predicted by the woke conditional predictor is retired. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off

PublicDescription: Indirect branch mis-predicted.This event counts when any indirect branch which can be predicted by the woke BTAC is retired, and has mispredicted for either the woke condition or the woke address. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off
BriefDescription: Indirect branch mis-predicted.This event counts when any indirect branch which can be predicted by the woke BTAC is retired, and has mispredicted for either the woke condition or the woke address. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off

PublicDescription: Indirect branch mis-predicted due to address mis-compare.This event counts when any indirect branch which can be predicted by the woke BTAC is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition, and has mispredicted the woke address. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off
BriefDescription: Indirect branch mis-predicted due to address mis-compare.This event counts when any indirect branch which can be predicted by the woke BTAC is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition, and has mispredicted the woke address. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off

PublicDescription: Conditional branch mis-predicted.This event counts when any branch which can be predicted by the woke conditional predictor is retired, and has mis-predicted the woke condition. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off. Conditional indirect branches which correctly predicted the woke condition but mis-predicted on the woke address do not count this event
BriefDescription: Conditional branch mis-predicted.This event counts when any branch which can be predicted by the woke conditional predictor is retired, and has mis-predicted the woke condition. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off. Conditional indirect branches which correctly predicted the woke condition but mis-predicted on the woke address do not count this event

PublicDescription: Indirect branch with predicted address executed.This event counts when any indirect branch which can be predicted by the woke BTAC is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off
BriefDescription: Indirect branch with predicted address executed.This event counts when any indirect branch which can be predicted by the woke BTAC is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off

PublicDescription: Procedure return with predicted address executed.This event counts when any procedure return which can be predicted by the woke CRS is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off
BriefDescription: Procedure return with predicted address executed.This event counts when any procedure return which can be predicted by the woke CRS is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition. This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off

This event still counts when branch prediction is disabled due to the woke MMU being off
BriefDescription: Procedure return mis-predicted due to address mis-compare.This event counts when any procedure return which can be predicted by the woke CRS is retired, was taken and correctly predicted the woke condition, and has mispredicted the woke address.
